OL,6,FLevlyn Andoh spoke with ITV Central
OL,7,Freporter Ravneet Nandra about her how
OL,8,Fher fathers injuries from the hit and
OL,9,Frun changed his life forever.
OL,11,FThe daughter of a man who was almost
OL,12,Fkilled by a hit-and-run driver in
OL,13,FBirmingham is urging police to do more
OL,14,Fto crack down on speeding.
OL,16,FLevlyn Andoh's father, Stephen, died
OL,17,Fin December last year from pneumonia,
OL,18,Fbut she believes his illness may be
OL,19,Flinked to the crash.
