OL,6,FOn the 17 May 2023, Stephen was
OL,7,Ffinishing his shift as a security
OL,8,Fguard in Birmingham.
OL,10,FA speeding driver on a 30mph road
OL,11,Fcrashed into the building Stephen was
OL,12,Fstanding at the junction of Birch Road
OL,13,Fand Cheshire Road.
OL,15,FHe escaped but with injuries to his
OL,16,Flegs. After surgery, he suffered blood
OL,17,Fclots which reached his lungs and
OL,18,Fheart.
OL,20,FStephen was then diagnosed with blood
OL,21,Fcancer and underwent chemotherapy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
