OL,6,FIn February 2024, his family said he
OL,7,Fhad been recovering. But his health
OL,8,Fsoon deteriorated, and he suffered
OL,9,Fmultiple chest infections and
OL,10,Fstruggled to walk and talk properly.
OL,12,FHe was admitted to hospital in
OL,13,FDecember 2024, and on the 27th, he
OL,14,Fdied from pneumonia. His family spent
OL,15,FChristmas at the hospital with him.
OL,17,FHis daughter Levlyn says doctors now
OL,18,Fbelieve her father's death may be
OL,19,Flinked to the crash.
