OL,6,FShe said: "Before the accident, my dad
OL,7,Fwas healthy, he was up and about, he
OL,8,Fcould work, we didn't need to do
OL,9,Fanything for him.
OL,11,F"But they did mention that it lay
OL,12,Fdormant in his body but it could have
OL,13,Flaid dormant for the rest of his life.
OL,14,FThey don't know, but the accident was
OL,15,Fdefinitely a trigger for everything to
OL,16,Fcome out the way it did.
