OL,6,F"It's frustrating because it's almost
OL,7,Ftwo years in May and nothings been
OL,8,Fdone about this. It's an ongoing
OL,9,Finvestigation but during this process
OL,10,FI've had to bury my father, whereas
OL,11,Fthis driver- whoever he is- is still
OL,12,Fout there potentially on the road.
OL,14,F"I just want justice for my dad. I
OL,15,Fwant the driver to take responsibility
OL,16,Ffor taking a father away from four
OL,17,Fkids, and a husband from a wife. I
OL,18,Fjust want him to understand the pain...
