OL,6,FIn a statement West Midlands Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our investigation continues
OL,8,Ffollowing a collision at the junction
OL,9,Fof Birch Road and Cheshire Road just
OL,10,Fbefore 11.45pm on 17 May 2023 where a
OL,11,Fman was seriously injured.
OL,13,F"We identified the driver and a man
OL,14,Fattended a voluntary interview under
OL,15,Fcaution on suspicion of causing
OL,16,Fserious injury by careless driving.
OL,17,FThe victim of the collision has since
OL,18,Fsadly died.
