OL,6,F"We have now passed a file of evidence
OL,7,Fon to the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,8,Fwho will decide if any charges should
OL,9,Fbe brought.
OL,11,FAccording to the RAC, the highest
OL,12,Fspeed recorded by the police force on
OL,13,Fa 30mph road between January 2023 and
OL,14,FAugust 2024 was 100mph.
OL,16,FAround 50 people are killed on West
OL,17,FMidlands roads each year, and another
OL,18,F1,000 injured.
