OL,6,FLevlyn's plea to police comes as the
OL,7,FPolice and Crime Commissioner for the
OL,8,FWest Midlands announced an investment
OL,9,Fof #190,000 into four mobile speed
OL,10,Fenforcement camera vans, bringing the
OL,11,Fforce's total to eight.
OL,13,FThey'll be dotted around hotspot areas
OL,14,Fin the region, aiming to crackdown on
OL,15,Fspeeding drivers.
OL,17,FBut ITV Central questioned the Police
OL,18,Fand Crime Commissioner Simon Foster at
OL,19,Fwhether the number of vans was too low.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
