OL,6,FHe said: "It's important to understand
OL,7,Fthat these mobile speed camera vans
OL,8,Fare deployed to particular hotspots.
OL,9,FThey are deployed to those key areas
OL,10,Fso they're not policing the entirety
OL,11,Fof the West Midlands, we're deploying
OL,12,Fthem to those areas where they can
OL,13,Fmake the biggest impact.
OL,15,F"And we ensure that those areas are
OL,16,Fidentified as a consequence to those
OL,17,Fareas where tragically there have been
OL,18,Fpeople killed and seriously injured.
